Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.45,0:22:54.20,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:23:02.67,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:10.84,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:19.02,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:25.96,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:36.37,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:45.98,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
